{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9f9fdea3fc","title":"对卡斯特罗关于发展中古关系的建议的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"17ef1e557a","index":0,"year":1959,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"9f9fdea3fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"7d3ba23944","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9f9fdea3fc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"卡斯特罗，当时任古巴武装部队总司令。"},{"id":"b1c6006317","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9f9fdea3fc","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央宣传部副部长姚漆1959年8月4日给外交部、外办、中联部的电报上。电报说，在古巴期间，卡斯特罗两次接见了我们。在谈到古巴和中国的关系时，他说应当把事情想得远一些，建议设法在哈瓦那的新华社机构中增加一位中国方面的较重要的人，作为中国的非正式的代表机构，进行宣传和各种联系工作。这样逐步把各种工作进行起来，将来水到渠成，就可以正式替代蒋介石方面驻古巴大使馆。"},{"id":"97a3c87bd5","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9f9fdea3fc","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈毅，当时任国务院副总理兼外交部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"58c918d8ab","type":"title","text":"对卡斯特罗叫关于发展中古关系的建议的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9f9fdea3fc"},{"id":"7d3ba23944","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来、陈毅同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9f9fdea3fc"},{"id":"b1c6006317","type":"paragraph","text":"这件事处理了没有？似宜派一位相当于公使或代办级的有政治买脑的同志去，以新华社分社长或记者资格驻古巴，是否可行，请酯。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9f9fdea3fc"},{"id":"97a3c87bd5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9f9fdea3fc"},{"id":"9f8265cbb2","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9f9fdea3fc"}],"page":{"id":"4eca8c0fea","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9